This is a list of notable [[antivirus software]] in the form of a comparison table.
<!--DO NOT add to the lists, use the comparison table-->
Most antiviruses consist of features like antiphishing or modes. Lots are just simple protection. However, most use behavioral blocking rather than virus signatures.
